# Ignore everything under .claude/ except project-local skills, which are
# checked in so the convention rides with the repo. Note: we cannot use
# a trailing-slash ignore on .claude/ here — gitignore will not re-include
# any path whose parent directory was excluded.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
.claude/worktrees/
